<h1>Pixel Clock</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Privacy Policy / 隐私政策</p>

<hr>

<h2>// Overview</h2>
<p>Pixel Clock is a pixel-art style clock app designed for iOS StandBy mode. We take your privacy seriously — in fact, we don't collect any of it.</p>
<p>Pixel Clock 是一款像素风格的时钟应用，专为 iOS 待机模式设计。我们非常重视您的隐私——事实上，我们不收集任何隐私数据。</p>

<h2>// Data Collection</h2>
<p><span class="highlight">We collect zero data.</span> Specifically:</p>
<ul>
    <li>No personal information</li>
    <li>No usage analytics or tracking</li>
    <li>No location data</li>
    <li>No cookies or identifiers</li>
    <li>No third-party SDKs or ad networks</li>
    <li>No network requests of any kind</li>
</ul>
<p>我们<span class="highlight">不收集任何数据</span>。具体来说：不收集个人信息、不进行使用分析或追踪、不获取位置数据、不使用 Cookie 或标识符、不集成第三方 SDK 或广告网络、不发起任何网络请求。</p>

<h2>// Data Storage</h2>
<p>Your settings (font style, time format, date display preference) are stored <span class="highlight">locally on your device only</span> using iOS built-in storage. This data never leaves your device.</p>
<p>您的设置（字体风格、时间格式、日期显示偏好）仅通过 iOS 内置存储<span class="highlight">保存在您的设备本地</span>。这些数据绝不会离开您的设备。</p>

<h2>// Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>Pixel Clock does not integrate any third-party services, analytics tools, crash reporters, or advertising frameworks. The app runs entirely offline.</p>
<p>Pixel Clock 未集成任何第三方服务、分析工具、崩溃报告或广告框架。应用完全离线运行。</p>

<h2>// Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>Pixel Clock does not collect data from anyone, including children under 13. The app is safe for users of all ages.</p>
<p>Pixel Clock 不收集任何人的数据，包括 13 岁以下儿童。本应用对所有年龄段的用户都是安全的。</p>

<h2>// Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>If we ever update this privacy policy, changes will be reflected on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
<p>如果我们更新本隐私政策，更改将在此页面上体现，并更新生效日期。</p>

